    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, preserved in showroom condition and curated for the most discerning collector. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, untouched interior, reflects a standard of care that is truly unparalleled. This is an investment-grade opportunity for an individual seeking automotive perfection and uncompromising mechanical integrity.",
